            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20plain%20of%20Shinar%2C%20the%20people%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20name%20for%20themselves%20by%20building%20a%20great%20tower.%20Their%20example%20shows%20the%20powerful%20forces%20of%20self-exaltation%20at%20work%20within%20the%20human%20race.%20God%20cannot%20share%20His%20glory%2C%20however%2C%20and%20will%20intentionally%20bring%20to%20naught%20any%20plan%20or%20project%20that%20overly%20exalts%20the%20name%20of%20humankind.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20opposite%20of%20such%20an%20exalted%20spirit%20can%20be%20seen%20in%20Abraham's%20life.%20Abraham%2C%20a%20lowly%20Aramaean%2C%20became%20the%20father%20of%20faith%20for%20all%20time.%20God%20promised%20him%2C%20%22I%20will%20cause%20you%20to%20become%20the%20father%20of%20a%20great%20nation.%20I%20will%20bless%20you%20and%20make%20you%20famous%2C%20and%20I%20will%20make%20you%20a%20blessing%20to%20others%22%20(Genesis%2012%3A2).%20Subsequent%20passages%20show%20how%20Abraham's%20simple%2C%20childlike%20obedience%20repeatedly%20attracted%20God's%20favor.%20He%20rose%20to%20higher%20and%20higher%20planes%20of%20honor%20by%20placing%20his%20faith%20solely%20in%20God.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EJesus%20said%20in%20Matthew%205%3A3%2C%20%22God%20blesses%20those%20who%20realize%20their%20need%20for%20him%2C%20for%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20Heaven%20is%20given%20to%20them.%22%20In%20verse%205%20He%20says%2C%20%22God%20blesses%20those%20who%20are%20gentle%20and%20lowly%2C%20for%20the%20whole%20earth%20will%20belong%20to%20them.%22%20What%20a%20contrast%20these%20attitudes%20are%20to%20those%20of%20the%20arrogant%20tower%20builders%20who%20tried%20to%20control%20the%20earth%20through%20their%20aggressiveness!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20psalmist%20said%2C%20%22With%20deepest%20awe%20I%20will%20worship%20at%20your%20Temple%22%20(Psalm%205%3A7).%20A%20temple%2C%20not%20a%20tower%2C%20is%20what%20we%20are%20building%2C%20and%20all%20its%20glory%20belongs%20to%20God%2C%20not%20to%20us!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
